<br>
Otherwise, I personally I think the bracer and earring are too important not to use most of the time unless you have something else for the focus effect.  There are situations where I won't be using DD spells like AE groups or going against a high-end mob with super resists.  But those don't happen very often, so 99% of the time if I am hunting I'll be wearing those 2 items.<br>
<br>
I don't use the ring 100% of the time, as casting faster isn't really a major factor in all situations.  I have the 7th shawl, so the FT is better for me than the focus mantle.  And regent conservation isn't a big priority for me on the necklace.<br>
<br>
